                "invention-title": [
                    "Uninterrupted solar thermally-driven system and method for preparing green hydrogen from ethanol",
                    "一种不间断的太阳能热驱动乙醇制绿氢系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an uninterrupted solar thermally-driven system and method for preparing green hydrogen from ethanol, and the system comprises a cold storage tank, a cold storage tank unloader, a particle type heat collector, a hot storage tank, a hot storage tank unloader, a heat exchange reactor, an evaporation heat exchanger, a particle circulator, a heliostat field, an auxiliary heating device, a feeding pump, a preheating heat exchanger and a tail gas separator, a cold storage tank discharge port, a cold storage tank discharger, a particle type heat collector, a heat storage tank, a heat storage tank discharger, a heat exchange reactor shell pass, an evaporation heat exchanger shell pass, a particle circulator and a cold storage tank feed port are sequentially connected and communicated. Sunlight reflected by the heliostat field irradiates the surface of the particle type heat collector. The auxiliary heating device is mounted on the heat storage tank; the feeding pump, the cold stream side of the preheating heat exchanger, the tube pass of the evaporation heat exchanger, the tube pass of the heat exchange reactor, the hot stream side of the preheating heat exchanger and the tail gas separator are sequentially connected and communicated. The continuous and stable solar hydrogen production process is realized by adopting a mode of firstly storing heat of solar energy and then utilizing the heat of the solar energy."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种不间断的太阳能热驱动乙醇制绿氢系统及方法，系统包括冷储罐、冷储罐卸料器、颗粒式集热器、热储罐、热储罐卸料器、换热反应器、蒸发换热器、颗粒循环器、定日镜场、辅热供热器、进料泵、预热换热器和尾气分离器，冷储罐出料口、冷储罐卸料器、颗粒式集热器、热储罐、热储罐卸料器、换热反应器壳程、蒸发换热器壳程、颗粒循环器和冷储罐进料口依次连接相通；定日镜场反射的太阳光照射在颗粒式集热器表面；辅热供热器安装在热储罐上；进料泵、预热换热器的冷流股侧、蒸发换热器管程、换热反应器管程、预热换热器的热流股侧和尾气分离器依次连接相通。本发明采用对太阳能的先储热、再利用形式，实现持续、稳定的太阳能制氢过程。"
                }
